                     <interp inst="t18121028-49-person649" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer of Bow-street. On the day the eagles were taken into Whitehall I saw Searle pick a gentleman's pocket of a handkerchief. He gave it to Harwood. I took them both in custody.</p>
               <p>Searle's Defence. I never had the handkerchief in my hand, nor never attempted to do such a thing.</p>
               <p>Harwood's Defence. I know nothing at all about the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>SEARLE, GUILTY, aged 20.</p>
               <p>HARWOOD, GUILTY, aged 17.</p>
               <p>
